media:group.media:description:
My landing: 7/10. Fabian's landing: 9/10. I fist fought him afterwards.

Shared cockpit landing at the old Hong Kong Kai Tak Int'l Airport (VHHX) after a grueling 10 minute flight from the new Hong Kong Chek Lap Kok Int'l Airport (VHHH). I came in fast and dumped flaps for a 7/10 landing followed by Fabian's solid 9/10. It was a good time.
